msgctxt "sn51.11:3.1"
msgid "Cittasamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti—"
msgstr "mental development …"

msgctxt "sn51.11:3.2"
msgid ""
"iti me cittaṃ na ca atilīnaṃ bhavissati, na ca atippaggahitaṃ bhavissati, na "
